r run.\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1991, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1755, \"end\": 1761, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Craig_Bryson\", \"score\": 0.8420344720297848, \"rank\": 0.18757711223724055, \"text\": \"Bryson\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Craig_Bryson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Craig_Bryson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two fences\", \"from\": 1785, \"to\": 1795}, {\"ngram\": \"round\", \"from\": 1820, \"to\": 1825}, {\"ngram\": \"the discipline\", \"from\": 1842, \"to\": 1856}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1877, \"to\": 1886}, {\"ngram\": \"the damage\", \"from\": 1919, \"to\": 1929}, {\"ngram\": \"the fencing bonus round\", \"from\": 1933, \"to\": 1956}, {\"ngram\": \"biathlon-style\", \"from\": 1966, \"to\": 1980}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am obviously really disappointed with my performance,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1993, \"to\": 2060, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my performance\", \"from\": 2034, \"to\": 2048}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I came here to try to get a medal and I really thought I was capable of one.\", \"from\": 2061, \"to\": 2138, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 2088, \"to\": 2095}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But I am also trying to be really positive and remember that I am an Olympian, I am also a doctor and I am also an army officer, so I have got other things going on, and sometimes you have to remember there is more to life than sport and medals.\\\"\", \"from\": 2140, \"to\": 2387, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2210, \"end\": 2218, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9993740833060102, \"rank\": 0.000626308698270054, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a doctor\", \"from